Xdebug installation

URL :  https://dev.to/jackmiras/xdebug-in-phpstorm-with-docker-2al8

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Chrome setup

Need to install Xdebug helper extension and enable

Setting | Extensions | Xdebug helper | Detail | Extensions Options | IDE KEY |

Select as PhpStorm => PHPSTORM

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

PHPSTORM IDE

Preferences | Build, Execution, Deployment | Docker

connection successful should show

Preferences | PHP | Debug | DBGp Proxy

IDE KEY : PHPSTORM
HOST    : Your host machine IP <$ipconfig getifaddr en0>
PORT    : 9000

Preferences | PHP | Servers

click +

Name    : <php-playground>
Host    : localhost
Port    : <according to docker-compose.yml, docker output port to host machine >
Debugger: Xdebug

check Use path mappings, according to your docker container path

Top right, click dropdown Edit Configurations

Select PHP Remote Debug

click +

Name : Docker

check Filter debug connection by IDE key

Sever                   : <php-playground>
IDE key (session id)    : PHPSTORM

**
click in he indicated button, and the debug button

